        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Filling Public Safety Vacancies Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bill provides additional funding for grants for the hiring and rehiring of additional career law enforcement officers under the Department of Justice's Community Oriented Policing Services (COPS) program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bill also requires law enforcement agencies that use the funds to hire or rehire a law enforcement officer to (1) perform a background check on the law enforcement officer, and (2) ensure that the law enforcement officer undergoes a psychological evaluation.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
